In  addition I  would like to thank all  who gave me encouragement over the
years for my efforts  to keep the  Aquarium  database up to date.  Not only
have your  suggestions caused  me to streamline the update process but they
have also pointed out the widespread usefulness of a tool such as Aquarium.

I  would  also like  to  offer  my  gratitude  to  the  nearly  one hundred
